I didn't know it was possible to spend 4k on a junk brand like wilwood. This isn't Hilow, but overpricedlo-lo. Still, the bigger parts are going to do much better with the thermal management.

If you have any interest in tracking your car, wheels, tires, and brakes are a great place to focus your money.
